spans.text: EER yet , ingenuous youth , thy steps retire From Cam's smooth margin , and the peaceful vale , Where Science called thee to her studious quire , And
thy friend ( and may he boast the name ) Breathe from his artless reed one parting lay ; A lay like this thy early Virtues claim , And this let voluntary Friendship pay
